<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>void_pixeler | Premium Design & Marketing</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:italic,wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #000; color: #fff; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        .hero-gradient { background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #111 0%, #000 100%); }
        .glass-card { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); transition: all 0.4s ease; }
        .glass-card:hover { border-color: #10b981; transform: translateY(-10px); background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05); }
        .text-glow { text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4); }
        .vp-logo { border: 2px solid #fff; padding: 10px 15px; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-style: italic; transition: 0.3s; }
        .vp-logo:hover { border-color: #10b981; color: #10b981; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 px-6 py-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md">
        <div class="vp-logo text-2xl tracking-tighter cursor-pointer">VP</div>
        <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest font-bold">
            <a href="#work" class="hover:text-emerald-500 transition">Work</a>
            <a href="#services" class="hover:text-emerald-500 transition">Services</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-emerald-500 transition text-emerald-500">Start a Project</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 hero-gradient overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>

        <div class="z-10">
            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-9xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4 text-glow">
                VOID<span class="text-emerald-500">_</span>PIXELER
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-2xl uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-light mb-10">
                Authentic Design • Strategic Marketing
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <a href="#work" class="px-10 py-4 bg-emerald-500 text-black font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white transition-all rounded-sm">Explore Portfolio</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="px-10 py-4 border border-white text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all rounded-sm">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto border-t border-white/10">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="p-10 glass-card">
                <h3 class="text-emerald-500 font-bold mb-4">01. BRANDING</h3>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Identity with Depth</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">I build visual systems that reflect the soul of your business, ensuring you stand out in the digital void.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-10 glass-card border-emerald-500/30">
                <h3 class="text-emerald-500 font-bold mb-4">02. MARKETING</h3>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Logic-Driven Ads</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Design that converts. I use consumer psychology to create ads that trigger immediate action and engagement.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-10 glass-card">
                <h3 class="text-emerald-500 font-bold mb-4">03. CREATIVE</h3>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Original Assets</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">From premium 3D-style food ads to corporate flyers, every pixel is original and human-crafted.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="work" class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#080808]">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-16">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-5xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tighter">Selected Works</h2>
                    <p class="text-emerald-500 mt-2 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs italic">Designs that move brands</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 aspect-[4/5]">
                    <img src="https://r.jina.ai/i/300483861c834bc6af1d94f29199c0da" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700" alt="Burger Ad">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-transparent to-transparent opacity-90 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end">
                        <span class="text-emerald-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Food Marketing</span>
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-1">Cravings Unleashed</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 aspect-[4/5]">
                    <img src="https://r.jina.ai/i/63442bc02ca24f749d031c26027a0033" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700" alt="Tech Training">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-transparent to-transparent opacity-90 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end">
                        <span class="text-emerald-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">EdTech Design</span>
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-1">PPTECH Systems</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 aspect-[4/5]">
                    <img src="https://r.jina.ai/i/3f35084922114251954845110901e855" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700" alt="Pizza Ad">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-transparent to-transparent opacity-90 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end">
                        <span class="text-emerald-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Direct Conversion</span>
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-1">Authentic Slices</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer id="contact" class="py-32 px-6 text-center border-t border-white/10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-none">Ready to start <br><span class="italic font-serif text-emerald-500 lowercase tracking-normal">your</span> story?</h2>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center mt-12">
                <div class="text-left px-8 py-4 border-l-2 border-emerald-500">
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest">Instagram</p>
                    <p class="text-lg font-bold">@void_pixeler</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-left px-8 py-4 border-l-2 border-emerald-500">
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest">Telegram</p>
                    <p class="text-lg font-bold">its_ayush-here</p>
                </div>
                <button class="bg-white text-black px-12 py-5 font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-emerald-500 hover:text-white transition-all rounded-full">
                    Let's Build Together
                </button>
            </div>

            <p class="mt-24 text-gray-600 text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] uppercase">© 2024 void_pixeler • Ayush • Pithoragarh, India</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
